rilled to announce that it now supports importing your Kindle highlights! This</p>\n            <footer class=\"gh-card-meta\">\n<!--\n             -->\n                    <span class=\"gh-card-author\">By Takuya Matsuyama</span>\n                    <time class=\"gh-card-date\" datetime=\"2025-02-21\">21 Feb 2025</time>\n                <!--\n         --></footer>\n        </div>\n    </a>","link":"https://www.devas.life/how-i-efficiently-built-a-browser-extension/","retrieved":1740096000000}]}